  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awakened by Death itself, you must ascend through a world shattered into floating islands and fragmented landscapes in <strong>Climb Quest</strong>. Though you weren't the first choice, you are now the realm's last hope. Your mission is to destroy the Crystal of Chaos—the destructive source tearing the realm apart—and restore peace to the fractured world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb Anything: Navigate a world where every surface is a potential path to victory. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooperative Play: Team up with friends to conquer challenges and unlock new paths. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision Platforming: Master challenging jumps and maneuvers as you ascend. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traps: Avoid traps designed to push you back and test your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Abilities: As you climb higher you unlock a new ability</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/d18a4e77f802d5e33146365227f35c1f.poster.avif?t=1759262791\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/d18a4e77f802d5e33146365227f35c1f.webm?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/d18a4e77f802d5e33146365227f35c1f.mp4?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this vertical adventure, every step counts. Navigate treacherous environments and master challenging platforming mechanics to uncover the hidden secrets of this shattered realm. Face powerful gusts of wind, collapsing platforms, and a variety of devious traps designed to push you back down. Utilize strategic teleportation runes and collect mystical artifacts that unlock hidden paths, enhancing your journey to stop the chaos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/cd78b86a8526aff39422a9c032a5d19b.poster.avif?t=1759262791\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/cd78b86a8526aff39422a9c032a5d19b.webm?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/cd78b86a8526aff39422a9c032a5d19b.mp4?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you climb alone or with friends, the fate of countless souls rests on your shoulders. Join the quest, ascend to greatness, and put an end to the destruction before it's too late!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your quest, defy the odds and vanquish the chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/879bb82947d0c3c71e1af9cb2abedaf9.poster.avif?t=1759262791\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/879bb82947d0c3c71e1af9cb2abedaf9.webm?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/879bb82947d0c3c71e1af9cb2abedaf9.mp4?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Awakened by Death itself, you must ascend through a world shattered into floating islands and fragmented landscapes in <strong>Climb Quest</strong>. Though you weren't the first choice, you are now the realm's last hope. Your mission is to destroy the Crystal of Chaos—the destructive source tearing the realm apart—and restore peace to the fractured world.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb Anything: Navigate a world where every surface is a potential path to victory. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooperative Play: Team up with friends to conquer challenges and unlock new paths. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision Platforming: Master challenging jumps and maneuvers as you ascend. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traps: Avoid traps designed to push you back and test your skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Abilities: As you climb higher you unlock a new ability</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/d18a4e77f802d5e33146365227f35c1f.poster.avif?t=1759262791\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/d18a4e77f802d5e33146365227f35c1f.webm?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/d18a4e77f802d5e33146365227f35c1f.mp4?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this vertical adventure, every step counts. Navigate treacherous environments and master challenging platforming mechanics to uncover the hidden secrets of this shattered realm. Face powerful gusts of wind, collapsing platforms, and a variety of devious traps designed to push you back down. Utilize strategic teleportation runes and collect mystical artifacts that unlock hidden paths, enhancing your journey to stop the chaos. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/cd78b86a8526aff39422a9c032a5d19b.poster.avif?t=1759262791\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/cd78b86a8526aff39422a9c032a5d19b.webm?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/cd78b86a8526aff39422a9c032a5d19b.mp4?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you climb alone or with friends, the fate of countless souls rests on your shoulders. Join the quest, ascend to greatness, and put an end to the destruction before it's too late!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your quest, defy the odds and vanquish the chaos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/879bb82947d0c3c71e1af9cb2abedaf9.poster.avif?t=1759262791\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/879bb82947d0c3c71e1af9cb2abedaf9.webm?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3151160/extras/879bb82947d0c3c71e1af9cb2abedaf9.mp4?t=1759262791\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
